com.interpss.core.acsc.fault
Interface AcscFaultPointRecord

All Superinterfaces:
AcscNetworkRef, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, NetworkRef, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AcscFaultPointRecordImpl
public interface AcscFaultPointRecord
extends AcscNetworkRef

A representation of the model object 'Result'. A class for recording fault point data.

The following features are supported:

  • ZFault
  • Fault Point V
  • Fault Sc Amps

See Also:
AcscFaultPackage.getAcscFaultPointRecord()
